name: Generate Script
func:
var message = msg.payload.message || "1526";
var message1 = msg.payload.message1 || "nil";
var message2 = msg.payload.message2 || "nil";
var message3 = msg.payload.message3 || "nil";
var message4 = msg.payload.message4 || "nil";
var message5 = msg.payload.message5 || "nil";
var message6 = msg.payload.message6 || "nil";
var message7 = msg.payload.message7 || "nil";
var message8 = msg.payload.message8 || "nil";
var message9 = msg.payload.message9 || "nil";
var message10 = msg.payload.message10 || "nil";
var message11 = msg.payload.message11 || "nil";
var message12 = msg.payload.message12 || "nil";
var message13 = msg.payload.message13 || "yes";
var message14 = msg.payload.message14 || "Number";
var message15 = msg.payload.message15 || "nil";
var message16 = msg.payload.message16 || "yes";
var message17 = msg.payload.message17 || "yes";

var script = `#!/bin/bash\n\n` +
    `IGATE_ID=${message}\n` +
    `UNIT_DESC="${message1}"\n` +
    `IGATE_PREFIX="iGatePlus"\n` +
    `IP="${message2}"\n` +
    `BROADCAST_IP="${message3}"\n` +
    `GATEWAY_IP="${message4}"\n` +
    `UNIT_SWITCH="on"\n` +
    `PORTAL_ID="245"\n` +
    `SERVER_URL="${message15}"\n` +
    `DHCP="no"\n` +
    `IGATE_ID_WITHOUT_PLANT_ID="80"\n` +
    `PORTAL_URL="${message15}"\n` +
    `\n` +
    `sqlite3 /opt/iplon/db/iPLON.sqlite <<END_SQL\n` +
    `.timeout 1;\n` +
    `delete from masters where config="SCADA=YES";\n` +
    `delete from masters where name="VirtualMasterLinux";\n` +
    `END_SQL\n` +
    `\n`;

if (message6 !== "nil") {
    script +=
        `sqlite3 /opt/iplon/db/iPLON.sqlite <<END_SQL\n` +
        `.timeout 1;\n` +
        `INSERT INTO masters values ("ModtcpMasterLinux","ethernet","${message6}","1","","SCADA=YES")\n` +
        `END_SQL\n`;
}
if (message7 !== "nil") {
    script +=
        `sqlite3 /opt/iplon/db/iPLON.sqlite <<END_SQL\n` +
        `.timeout 1;\n` +
        `INSERT INTO masters values ("ModtcpMasterLinux","ethernet","${message7}","2","","SCADA=YES")\n` +
        `END_SQL\n`;
}
if (message8 !== "nil") {
    script +=
        `sqlite3 /opt/iplon/db/iPLON.sqlite <<END_SQL\n` +
        `.timeout 1;\n` +
        `INSERT INTO masters values ("ModtcpMasterLinux","ethernet","${message8}","3","","SCADA=YES")\n` +
        `END_SQL\n`;
}
if (message9 !== "nil") {
    script +=
        `sqlite3 /opt/iplon/db/iPLON.sqlite <<END_SQL\n` +
        `.timeout 1;\n` +
        `INSERT INTO masters values ("ModtcpMasterLinux","ethernet","${message9}","4","","SCADA=YES")\n` +
        `END_SQL\n`;
}
if (message10 !== "nil") {
    script +=
        `sqlite3 /opt/iplon/db/iPLON.sqlite <<END_SQL\n` +
        `.timeout 1;\n` +
        `INSERT INTO masters values ("ModtcpMasterLinux","ethernet","${message10}","5","","SCADA=YES")\n` +
        `END_SQL\n`;
}
if (message11 !== "nil") {
    script +=
        `sqlite3 /opt/iplon/db/iPLON.sqlite <<END_SQL\n` +
        `.timeout 1;\n` +
        `INSERT INTO masters values ("ModtcpMasterLinux","ethernet","${message11}","6","","SCADA=YES")\n` +
        `END_SQL\n`;
}
if (message12 !== "nil") {
    script +=
        `sqlite3 /opt/iplon/db/iPLON.sqlite <<END_SQL\n` +
        `.timeout 1;\n` +
        `INSERT INTO masters values ("ModtcpMasterLinux","ethernet","${message12}","7","","SCADA=YES")\n` +
        `END_SQL\n`;
}
if (message13 == "yes") {
    script +=
        `sqlite3 /opt/iplon/db/iPLON.sqlite <<END_SQL\n` +
        `.timeout 1;\n` +
        `INSERT INTO masters values ("ModbusMasterLinux","/dev/ttyUS","1","${message14}","","SCADA=YES")\n` +
        `END_SQL\n`;
}
if (message16 == "yes") {
    script +=
        `sqlite3 /opt/iplon/db/iPLON.sqlite <<END_SQL\n` +
        `.timeout 1;\n` +
        `INSERT INTO sending values ("/mnt/jffs2/dglog", "main", "main", "iplon")\n` +
        `END_SQL\n`;
}
script +=

    `\n` +
    `echo "All most the work has completed...."\n` +
    `\n` +
    `cp hostname /etc/
chmod 777 /etc/hostname
chown root:root /etc/hostname\n` +
    `\n` +
    `cp hosts /etc/
chmod 777 /etc/hosts
chown root:root /etc/hosts\n` +
    `\n` +
    `cp cron/crontabs/iplon /var/spool/cron/crontabs/iplon
chmod 777 /var/spool/cron/crontabs/iplon
chown crontab:crontab /var/spool/cron/crontabs/iplon\n` +
    `\n` +
    `cp iplon/jffs2/solar/y.sh /opt/iplon/jffs2/solar
chmod 777 /opt/iplon/jffs2/solar/y.sh
chown iplon:iplon /opt/iplon/jffs2/solar/y.sh\n` +
    `\n` +
    `cp iplon/jffs2/solar/yasdi.lua /opt/iplon/jffs2/solar
chmod 777 /opt/iplon/jffs2/solar/yasdi.lua
chown iplon:iplon /opt/iplon/jffs2/solar/yasdi.lua\n` +
    `\n` +
    `cp -r iplon/jffs2/solar/lua /opt/iplon/jffs2/solar
chmod -R 777 /opt/iplon/jffs2/solar/lua
chown -R iplon:iplon /opt/iplon/jffs2/solar/lua\n` +
    `\n` +
    `chmod -R 777 /opt/iplon/scripts
chown -R iplon:iplon /opt/iplon/scripts\n` +
    `\n` +
    `echo "Now we can start to edit the Sqlite Database..."\n` +
    `\n` +

    `sqlite3 /opt/iplon/db/iPLON.sqlite <<END_SQL\n` +
    `.timeout 1;\n` +
    `INSERT INTO sending values ("/mnt/jffs2/dglog","main","main","iplon");\n` +
    `UPDATE unit SET value = $IGATE_ID WHERE field = "id";\n` +
    `UPDATE unit SET value = "$UNIT_DESC" WHERE field = "desc";\n` +
    `UPDATE unit SET value = "$IGATE_PREFIX" WHERE field = "hostname";\n` +
    `UPDATE unit SET value = "$UNIT_SWITCH" WHERE field = "switch";\n` +
    `UPDATE unit SET value = "$PORTAL_ID" WHERE field = "portalId";\n` +
    `UPDATE unit SET value = "$PORTAL_URL" WHERE field = "portal";\n` +
    `UPDATE ips SET ip = "$IP" WHERE id = 1;\n` +
    `UPDATE ips SET broadcast = "$BROADCAST_IP" WHERE id = 1;\n` +
    `UPDATE connection SET value = "$GATEWAY_IP" WHERE field = "gw";\n` +
    `UPDATE unit SET value = "$SERVER_URL" WHERE field = "server";\n` +
    `UPDATE connection SET value = "$DHCP" WHERE field = "dhcp";\n` +
    `UPDATE unit SET value = "$IGATE_ID_WITHOUT_PLANT_ID" WHERE field = "switchNumber";\n` +
    `DELETE FROM cfgdata;\n` +
    `END_SQL\n` +
    `\n` +

    `echo "Setting up default configuration changes"\n` +
    `echo $IGATE_PREFIX$IGATE_ID > /etc/hostname\n` +
    `echo "127.0.0.1       localhost" > /etc/hosts\n` +
    `echo "127.0.1.1       "$IGATE_PREFIX$IGATE_ID >> /etc/hosts\n` +
    `\n`;

if (message16 == "yes")
{
    script +=
    `if [ ! -d "/opt/iplon/jffs2/dglog" ]; then
   mkdir /opt/iplon/jffs2/dglog
   fi
   chmod 777 /opt/iplon/jffs2/dglog
   chown iplon:iplon /opt/iplon/jffs2/dglog\n` +
    `\n`;
}
script +=

    `echo "Setting up ourzone to IST"\n` +
    `sudo echo "Asia/Kolkata" > /etc/timezone\n` +
    `sudo dpkg-reconfigure tzdata\n` +
    `\n` +
    `echo "Setting up Cron Scripts"\n` +
    `touch /var/spool/cron/crontabs/root
    chmod 777 /var/spool/cron/crontabs/root
    chown crontab:crontab /var/spool/cron/crontabs/root\n` +
    `echo "*/10 * * * * /opt/iplon/scripts/persistenceRestore.sh >> /var/log/iplon/y.log 2&>1" > /var/spool/cron/crontabs/root\n` +
    `echo " " >> /var/spool/cron/crontabs/root\n` +
    `echo "@reboot /opt/iplon/scripts/persistenceRestore.sh restore >> /var/log/iplon/y.log 2&>1" >> /var/spool/cron/crontabs/root\n` +
    `echo " " >> /var/spool/cron/crontabs/root\n` + 
    `echo "30 5 * * * cd /opt/iplon/ && truncate -s 0 *.1 && truncate -s 0 *.log && cd" >> /var/spool/cron/crontabs/root\n` +
    `echo " " >> /var/spool/cron/crontabs/root\n` + 
    `echo "30 3 * * * sudo reboot" >> /var/spool/cron/crontabs/root\n` +
    `echo " " >> /var/spool/cron/crontabs/root\n` + 
    `echo "*/2 * * * * /opt/iplon/scripts/i_edge_data_push.sh" >> /var/spool/cron/crontabs/root\n` +
    `echo " " >> /var/spool/cron/crontabs/root\n` + 
    `echo "*/15 * * * * /opt/iplon/scripts/iplon_vpn.sh" >> /var/spool/cron/crontabs/root\n` +
    `echo " " >> /var/spool/cron/crontabs/root\n` + 
    `\n` +
    `echo "Setting up Hardware and Software Time Sync..."\n` +
    `\n` +
    `systemctl restart iplon-bl\n` +
    `sudo reboot\n`;
msg.payload = script;
return msg;

name: top-bar logo
format:
<style>
    #top-bar-logo {
    background-image: url(https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/D4E0BAQHd8FmvwMrq_g/company-logo_200_200/0/1665037560142?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=-0WBInLRgZxo-HCsp13qFHOJJ2MiovcPO-bwY56xkiE);
    background-size: 120px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: 1600px;
    height: 65px;
    width: 1800px;
}
</style>

<script id="logo-script" type="text/javascript">
function build(){
    $("#top-bar-logo").remove()
    var logo = $('<div />').attr("id","top-bar-logo");
    var topbar = $('.md-toolbar-tools');
    topbar.append(logo)
}
function checkExistence(){
    console.log($("#top-bar-logo"))
    if($("#top-bar-logo").length > 0){
        return
    }
    build()
    setTimeout(checkExistence,100)
}

build()
setTimeout(checkExistence,100)
</script>
